Ingrediënts EASY TO MAKE
4 cups Italian Flour (1.1 lb/500g)
2 teaspoons Fast Action Dried Yeast (7g)
1 ⅓ cups Lukewarm Water (320ml)
1 tablespoon Olive Oil
1 pinch pinch Salt
½ teaspoon Sugar
add Regular Flour (or semolina, for dusting)
2 balls Mozzarella (250g)
½ cup Gorgonzola (100g)
½ cup Goat Cheese (120g)
½ cup Parmesan (freshly grated, 40g)
½ cup Strained Tomatoes (crushed, passata, 200g)
add Black Pepper (optional)
